What you need to know:

Cherono, the Boston and Chicago Marathon champion, will have World marathon champion Amos Kipruto, Evans Chebet, former two-time world marathon champion Abel Kirui for company as they battle for supremacy on the streets of the Spanish cityKipruto - who has been training in Kapsabet, Nandi County on his part - said that he will be looking forward to a fast race and he is targeting on improving on his  personal best timeIt won’t be a walk in the park for Kenyan athletes given that they will be competing against Ethiopians who have better times notably Birhanu Legese (2:02:48)